    (())))
; Evaluation took 1.53 milliseconds.
Deterministic: Empty

  ; Action: load=metta_atom('&self',=,[increment],[superpose,[[do,['change-state!','&var',[+,1,['get-state','&var']]]],['get-state','&var']]])
(= 
  (increment) 
  (superpose 
    ( (do 
        (change-state! &var 
          (+ 1 
            (get-state &var)))) 
      (get-state &var))))

      (increment))) 
  ( (sequential 
      ( (do 
          (State 8)) 
        (do 
          (State 8)))) 
    (sequential

      (2 2))))
